{"tid":2174294,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人直覺上抗拒炒股票","createTime":"2020-08-25T21:42:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T10:16:09.000Z","uid":58316,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"61079b5f669c283c20af838b77f5d0347e0d74ec","tid":2174294,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T21:42:17.000Z","msg":"貼過幾隻<br />\n有隻半年內個位升雙位<br />\n有隻翻左番<br />\n仲有100蚊微升幾蚊<br />\n但始終冇玩<br />\n好似心掛掛咁<br />\n你話做依行工作需要<br />\n或者師奶買黎係咁倚玩下<br />\n同打牌一樣嗜好<br />\n同人打牙較有話題交流心得<br />\n就話<br />\n好似從心底裏覺得<br />\n一個男仔<br />\n揸住舊錢睇升升跌跌<br />\n若有所失咁<br />\n好似好傻<br />\n本大其實只係數字遊戲<br />\n本少更加冇pt<br />\n哂埋d心機時間<br />\n一個浪冚埋黎<br />\n身體有事<br />\n一切歸零<br />\n如果咁啱做正依d工<br />\n就當係份工<br />\n幫公司幫客買<br />\n但自己冇position"},{"pid":"16e5ddf7ae00022c7e69c3b37d6763d973d29635","tid":2174294,"uid":228793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T23:18:09.000Z","msg":"唔緊要啦 贏又好輸又好 d野都返唔到來"},{"pid":"cf8d038a2faa3f98ba2d4b89d31017c37168137a","tid":2174294,"uid":82398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T23:28:23.000Z","msg":"有人鍾意腳踏實地<br />\n有人鍾意投機取巧<br />\n有錢無錢都係咁過<br />\n有人賺大錢亦有人輸身家"},{"pid":"82badbbd4eb5697e879d8f11013b99ba684da57f","tid":2174294,"uid":62900,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T23:30:46.000Z","msg":"成日都覺得自己會扑中一隻股升幾十倍 <br />\n一夜致富<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c69081a1f10e4fb4159b3d44d61eba59cb3c7cc","tid":2174294,"uid":111322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T23:33:54.000Z","msg":"人生太短 出手要夠大"},{"pid":"4dad09896cea86c554194e3202cb819108f6d97d","tid":2174294,"uid":143321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T00:43:30.000Z","msg":"日日都睇<br />\n但起碼已經兩年冇買"},{"pid":"8fea97a6e9f697d8faddae33d4ecee8f73f7e6e4","tid":2174294,"uid":69168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T00:48:17.000Z","msg":"all in咩，搏下之嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma